XSS Vulnerability:

Description:

“user_id” parameter is not sanitized, that leads to reflected xss.

POC:

https://0x62626262.files.wordpress.com/2016/01/wpsymposiumpro16_1xsspoc.png

Fix:
Update to version 16.01.01

